Options in the configuration file:

Sections:

[source]
1. The directories to tar up. (section: directories) - convert to absolute paths. Python List format.
2. Directories and files to exclude (wildcards acceptable). Python List format.

[destination]
1. The tar filename
2. Compression type (default: gz), if empty do not compress.


[misc]
1. Verbose output?
2. Exclude version control system directories.


